Nancheng...

11
00:02:57,980 --> 00:02:59,120
Go...

12
00:03:00,410 --> 00:03:01,250
Go...

13
00:03:35,300 --> 00:03:38,220
(Warning: Radiation.
Do not enter when the light is on.)

14
00:03:44,730 --> 00:03:45,820
Don't worry.

15
00:03:46,290 --> 00:03:47,450
They're just taking a scan.

16
00:03:48,266 --> 00:03:49,920
The doctors inside will look after her.

17
00:03:57,770 --> 00:03:58,620
Come.

18
00:03:58,820 --> 00:03:59,660
Sit for a bit.

19
00:04:07,060 --> 00:04:07,900
Sibei.

20
00:04:08,977 --> 00:04:10,380
About your mom's hospital stay,

21
00:04:11,610 --> 00:04:13,610
don't put too much pressure on yourself.

22
00:04:16,733 --> 00:04:18,900
If she wants you
to go to the provincial capital,

23
00:04:18,900 --> 00:04:19,740
you should go.

24
00:04:19,844 --> 00:04:20,900
I'll handle things here.

25
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:24,170
With Mom like this,

26
00:04:24,980 --> 00:04:26,020
I can't leave.

27
00:04:27,511 --> 00:04:29,610
You don't trust me
to take care of her, do you?

28
00:04:34,980 --> 00:04:35,820
Well...

29
00:04:36,490 --> 00:04:37,330
You're right.

30
00:04:39,580 --> 00:04:40,420
All these years,

31
00:04:41,490 --> 00:04:43,220
I've never done anything

32
00:04:43,220 --> 00:04:44,688
that could make you feel at ease.

33
00:04:45,170 --> 00:04:46,010
Not once.

34
00:05:02,580 --> 00:05:03,420
Sibei.

35
00:05:05,340 --> 00:05:06,290
When you were born,

36
00:05:08,220 --> 00:05:09,490
I was the one who urged your mom

37
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,340
to send you to the countryside.

38
00:05:12,490 --> 00:05:13,490
All these years,

39
00:05:14,490 --> 00:05:17,020
you've always thought your mom
was against you in everything,

40
00:05:17,020 --> 00:05:18,220
blamed you for everything,

41
00:05:18,900 --> 00:05:20,170
and favored Nianwen

42
00:05:20,170 --> 00:05:21,010
over you.

43
00:05:22,020 --> 00:05:23,460
But the truth behind it all...

44
00:05:24,340 --> 00:05:25,410
It was because of me.

45
00:05:31,410 --> 00:05:32,580
Your mom's illness

46
00:05:33,980 --> 00:05:34,820
made me suddenly

47
00:05:35,410 --> 00:05:37,490
realize a lot of things.

48
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,688
I used to blame her for her temper.

49
00:05:41,955 --> 00:05:43,850
But someone
who had to feed the whole family...

50
00:05:44,170 --> 00:05:45,410
If she weren't strong-willed,

51
00:05:46,460 --> 00:05:48,410
how could we have lived
the life we have now?

52
00:05:50,290 --> 00:05:51,460
I've wronged your mom.

53
00:05:52,850 --> 00:05:53,690
And I've wronged you.

54
00:05:55,930 --> 00:05:57,540
You've suffered too much because of me.

55
00:05:58,290 --> 00:05:59,220
Dad, stop talking.

56
00:06:05,250 --> 00:06:06,140
It's time.

57
00:06:07,410 --> 00:06:08,250
This family

58
00:06:10,088 --> 00:06:11,850
needs me to take responsibility too.

59
00:06:13,930 --> 00:06:14,770
As a husband,

60
00:06:15,580 --> 00:06:16,420
as a father,

61
00:06:17,755 --> 00:06:19,266
I've been absent for too long.

62
00:06:20,410 --> 00:06:21,250
Sibei,

63
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:22,930
listen to your mom.

64
00:06:23,266 --> 00:06:24,570
Go to the provincial capital.

65
00:06:25,050 --> 00:06:26,410
Start a new life there.

66
00:06:27,580 --> 00:06:28,540
I'm here.

67
00:06:29,370 --> 00:06:30,210
Dad's here.

68
00:06:31,044 --> 00:06:32,250
Don't worry.

69
